    faq3q: "Is an asbestos certificate also mandatory for rental?",
    faq3a: "Currently, the asbestos certificate is <strong>not yet mandatory for rental</strong>. However, the Flemish government has plans to <strong>extend the obligation to rental properties</strong> in the future. It is therefore wise to have an asbestos certificate drawn up now for your rental properties.",
    faq4q: "What if asbestos is found?",
